56: 509. 1999) indicated material in LINN as the type of 
<taxonomicName authority="(L.) Moench" authorityName="Moench" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1771" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Sorghum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bicolor">
