<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="575">Taxon</emphasis>
50: 577. 2001) have, however, accepted Poilecot as having effectively typified the name using the Clifford sheet. This, however, was ineffective, and 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Davidseâ€™s">Davidse's</normalizedToken>
